# Lets start by checking my inventory.
# We have some basic resources. Let's move to the nearest coal and begin mining.
# We will move to nearest coal resource using move_to and mining the coal using the burner mining drill.
# Once we have mined 100 coal, we will stop mining coal.
coal1 = nearest('coal')
move_to(coal1)
while check_inventory()["coal"] < 100:
    harvest_resource(coal1, quantity=1)  # Harvest coal
    observe_nature()  # Look around for other resources and plan next move
    if check_inventory()["coal"] == 100:
        break  # Exit the loop once we have mined 100 coal
